//   - input mem_region dst  (lock from dst_pool)
//   - rand bit [15:0] length
//
// Constraints:
//   - length must be > 0
//   - length must be a power of 2 (hint: length & (length - 1) == 0)
//   - length must be <= 4096
//   - src.base_addr != dst.base_addr (no overlap)
//
// exec body SV: Write src_addr, dst_addr, length to DMA registers
// exec body C:  Write to memory-mapped DMA registers
// ======================================================

